Use the standard library
This is how to greatest_common_divisor of a and b:
   Remember that x is abs of a
   Remember that y is abs of b
   Do this 1000 times:
      When y is 0, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      Remember that r is remainder of x and y
      Remember that x is y
      Remember that y is r
   End do
   The answer is x
Now you know
>>> greatest_common_divisor of 3 and 5
1
>>> greatest_common_divisor of 25 and 15
5
>>> greatest_common_divisor of 3 and 7
1